Takealot’s gift voucher giveaways on MyBroadband continue, with vouchers worth R3,000 up for grabs this week. Over six months, Takealot will give away vouchers to the total of R48,000 on MyBroadband – with R29,000 in vouchers already won. To enter the competition, browse the Takealot website, choose a product you would like to put a gift voucher towards, and post it in the competition thread on the MyBroadband forum. The rules and entry requirements are explained on the MyBroadband forum. Entrants stand a chance to win a R2,000 or R1,000 Takealot voucher. This week’s giveaway closes on 30 June 2017.